snippet.title: Contain Wishlist Teaser
snippet.description:
Contain is a first-person cooperative tactical shooter with in-depth character and gun customization. Contain requires calculated teamwork, Practice your tactics and test your equipment before the mission.

There is an organization that directs many task forces that are trying to control objects of supernatural origin that have fallen from space. The story centers on a special task force called the Giants.

We are happy to announce that our Steam Store Page, Discord Server is live!

Steam Store: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2186700/Contain/

Discord: https://discord.gg/adqEbdf476
